{"type": "article", "id": 12031, "title": "这座两百米高的大楼，设计灵感是碧昂丝的音乐", "description": "你没看错，就是那个会唱歌的碧昂丝。", "date": "2015-07-14T09:00:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 12871, "name": "高楼"}, {"id": 12872, "name": "墨尔本"}, {"id": 2062, "name": "碧昂丝"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605213725kgj7PHAJY8xqeIV3.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t现在的建筑师为了推介自己的建筑作品也是拼了。<a href=\"%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E6%8E%A8%E4%BB%8B%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E6%8B%BC%E5%95%A6%E3%80%82%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BA%8B%E5%8A%A1%E6%89%80Elenberg%20Fraser%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E8%AF%B4%E8%AF%B4%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%96%E4%BB%AC%E5%88%9A%E5%88%9A%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E7%9A%84%E6%91%A9%E5%A4%A9%E5%A4%A7%E6%A5%BC%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%8C%E7%81%B5%E6%84%9F%E6%BA%90%E4%BA%8E%E7%A2%A7%E6%98%82%E6%96%AF%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E6%94%AF%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90%E5%BD%95%E5%BD%B1%E5%B8%A6%E3%80%82\" target=\"_blank\">澳大利亚建筑事务所 Elenberg Fraser </a>最近通过了一个摩天大楼设计方案，设计师说他们的设计灵感源于碧昂丝的一支音乐录影带。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213720X8hl6KT4eQAMikHV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t建筑概念图，最高的就是我们提到的这幢楼了\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这幢建筑名叫 <span>Premiere Tower</span>，建成后将坐落于墨尔本斯宾塞街的 <span>134 </span>号。设计师说，外立面的一系列曲线和凸起灵感源于碧昂丝 <span>2013 </span>年的音乐录影带《<span>Ghost</span>》。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213720tGLEmBYzybRP69nT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t外立面的细节\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213721EJqOTIz10SAkKsQ2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t一层的设计<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213721Sv8PbytR53AFkoJn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t室内设计\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213722GMVwgsFiKYeb89lt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t室内的梁柱也设计的颇有动感\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213722RVWEqHaQ4sCJuIKO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t观景房\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052137238yFIwMAqvL54T3oW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213723oKCTOhBwyrudm6VA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t建筑师在接受媒体的采访时说，“我们要向更有审美的东西表达敬意。”这幢楼建成后，将有 <span>68 </span>层高，将包含 <span>660 </span>个公寓和 <span>160 </span>个酒店房间。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605213724gPApMlvixsmVqrYW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t扭动的身躯\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052137245NVuMEJgbHTsq0ki.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t建筑概念图\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t有人认为这个大楼<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2015/07/06/premiere-tower-beyonce-inspired-skyscraper-melbourne-elenberg-fraser/\" target=\"_blank\">和加拿大的的沙漏状摩天大楼很相似</a>，那幢大楼是由 MAD 工作室设计的，于 2012 年建成，被当地居民戏称为“玛丽莲·梦露大厦”。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052137258LGzMt2KERus4dwi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5921875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tMAD 工作室设计的沙漏状大楼\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<iframe src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XNjY0MDM1NDU2\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n\t</iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t这就是碧昂丝 《Ghost》的 MV 了\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><em><a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2015/07/06/premiere-tower-beyonce-inspired-skyscraper-melbourne-elenberg-fraser/\" target=\"_blank\">dezeen</a></em>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}